title: Dev SuperPowers: OnlineASP.NET Identity using vNext
eventShortDescription:
​Make the most of ASP.NET vNext with ASP.NET Identity 2, OWIN and Dependency Injection

Previous versions of ASP.NET Membership have left a bad taste in many developers mouths, and some are now dangerously out of date. 

Watch Ben Cull take you through the latest, greatest and safest way to get your membership system up and running using ASP.NET Identity, OWIN and Dependency Injection.
